{"tid":2451184,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 官方曝「超萌團員」嘟嘴獨照！網驚：怎麼那麼像子瑜","createTime":"2021-03-18T02:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T06:05:36.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"42e594fb15aacec4eed680e8bffd5e9d697fc89f","tid":2451184,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2021/03/17/210317-15829-1-1RkOQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F210317-15829-1-1RkOQ.jpg&h=801da282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE 官方 IG 分享了多賢的穿搭照，被發現跟周子瑜彷彿雙胞胎。<br />\n<br />\n昨天（16日）TWICE 官方 IG 帳號 PO 出數張多賢的個人穿搭照，而第一張嘟嘴賣萌的 POSE，被網友發現跟子瑜好像，掀起了留言串「好像雙胞胎」。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE 一共有九位成員，但最為台灣粉絲熟知的莫過於台灣成員周子瑜，新聞焦點總是在子瑜身上，然昨天晚上 TWICE 官方 IG 分享了數張單一成員的穿搭照，身穿墨綠色針織上衣搭配黑色過膝裙，身上背著 CELINE 帆布包，屬非常可愛的穿搭照。而網友發現這位團員乍看跟周子瑜有點像，尤其是擺在第一張的嘟嘴表情，翻出子瑜做同樣表情的萌照，發現相似度極高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2021/03/17/210317-15829-2-qBs7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F210317-15829-2-qBs7E.jpg&h=e51a6b62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多賢的穿搭照讓她看起來越來越成熟了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2021/03/17/210317-15829-3-PjDYg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F210317-15829-3-PjDYg.jpg&h=6203d54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一系列多賢穿搭照中，有一張嘟嘴的表情，被網友發現跟子瑜好像。<br />\n<br />\n這位穿搭照的主角是 TWICE 的韓籍成員多賢，跟周子瑜也是好朋友，平時最引人矚目的是她多變的髮色，過去常以紫色、粉紅色等特殊色為造型，因此這張黑色髮的造型，加上嘟嘴表情會被誤認成是子瑜。<br />\n<br />\n粉絲看到照片後紛紛留言表示「第一張真的好像子瑜喔」、「多賢變成熟了，黑髮很適合她」、「兩個人都很可愛，但子瑜更可愛一些」、「TWICE 本來就都是美女啊」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2021/03/17/210317-15829-4-KnQt1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F210317-15829-4-KnQt1.jpg&h=ebed90e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多賢過去髮色多變，這次染回黑髮，難怪讓她看起來跟子瑜撞型。"},{"pid":"a838b8e5fb8d2ff5bdcf8ceed6274623a1913ac7","tid":2451184,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:17:37.000Z","msg":"腎b....<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5160f295475ba05a969ea40b48a2f13775e578f","tid":2451184,"uid":255310,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"腎b正式好多..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10efce8a655527fad5cc32d6560670ccca4caf5c","tid":2451184,"uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:22:43.000Z","msg":"多醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4067e483bb9e2b0ca63fb0de5a4b29567fba5d1c","tid":2451184,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e5160f295475ba05a969ea40b48a2f13775e578f","tid":2451184,"uid":255310,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"腎b正式好多..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:23:10.000Z","msg":"整咗又"},{"pid":"9a1c925184f23433396f24977c70111b27e8c0c7","tid":2451184,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"10efce8a655527fad5cc32d6560670ccca4caf5c","tid":2451184,"uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:22:43.000Z","msg":"多醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:23:38.000Z","msg":"你食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9949d3db362218e9768055a5a9aadb822345ef79","tid":2451184,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:26:01.000Z","msg":"腎b點睇都靚過條咸魚啦"},{"pid":"6e6f7a65fade0d29e49a314c4fb9266e88a21919","tid":2451184,"uid":255172,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cit